     outlevs.lev 
*HIT
     hitran.hit
*SFC
     300 1  ! surface t, reflectance
*RAD 
      ./out/rad_*.asc  ! radiance files
*OPT 
      ./out/opt_*.asc  ! optical depth files
*TAB
      ./out/tab/tab_*.asc ! lookup tables
*LUT  
      ./out/tab/tab_*.asc
*END
